00:26:26,057 --> 00:26:26,517
Hi.

440
00:26:26,517 --> 00:26:28,618
Beautiful game, Unravel.

441
00:26:28,618 --> 00:26:31,280
I haven't played it, but it's a beautiful game.

442
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:36,183
What I got from this is that Unravel is a game

443
00:26:36,183 --> 00:26:38,465
about empathy for oneself.

444
00:26:38,465 --> 00:26:41,086
So you play this game, and probably you

445
00:26:41,086 --> 00:26:42,927
project yourself onto a wall.

446
00:26:44,548 --> 00:26:46,149
I don't remember, Yarny.

447
00:26:46,149 --> 00:26:50,930
And so this is a game that helps you probably self-heal.

448
00:26:50,930 --> 00:26:56,172
It probably was a healing journey for you as well.

