470
00:28:53,382 --> 00:29:00,285
It's not really for me to say because I'm not the most technically minded person.

471
00:29:00,285 --> 00:29:05,587
I certainly wouldn't mind, like every platform we can be on is nice.

472
00:29:05,587 --> 00:29:09,989
Just make it more accessible for young children to have it on their device.

473
00:29:09,989 --> 00:29:10,690
Yes, but...

474
00:29:10,690 --> 00:29:13,991
Okay, thank you.

475
00:29:16,325 --> 00:29:21,947
Hi, I just wanted to ask, for a game whose narrative is so strongly visual,

476
00:29:21,947 --> 00:29:23,148
what was the writing process like?

477
00:29:23,148 --> 00:29:27,410
Did it involve lots of storyboarding, or photography, or mood boards,

478
00:29:27,410 --> 00:29:31,432
or a combination of all different sorts of elements?

479
00:29:31,432 --> 00:29:35,354
Photography was very much a big part of it.

480
00:29:35,354 --> 00:29:38,995
It sort of started with how the concept was created.

481
00:29:42,504 --> 00:29:52,647
Basically, I mean, I don't know if you've heard this, but I was out camping in the woods and made this little doll and just ran around with it and started taking pictures of it doing strange things.

482
00:29:52,647 --> 00:30:00,130
Because I didn't have any other tools except for camera and what I could find.

483
00:30:00,130 --> 00:30:03,331
So photography was always like a big part of the process.

484
00:30:03,331 --> 00:30:05,752
And.

485
00:30:06,547 --> 00:30:09,847
since the whole thing about family bonds

486
00:30:09,847 --> 00:30:14,408
was also such an important part right from the start,

487
00:30:14,408 --> 00:30:17,069
I actually started with our photo albums.

488
00:30:17,069 --> 00:30:21,310
So a lot of the content was not actually created

489
00:30:21,310 --> 00:30:24,131
for the gamers, which is things that I found

490
00:30:24,131 --> 00:30:29,932
that felt appropriate.

491
00:30:29,932 --> 00:30:33,233
So it was more, yeah, I don't know, I'm rambling a bit,

492
00:30:33,233 --> 00:30:35,953
but it was pretty much like.

493
00:30:36,652 --> 00:30:40,634
my photo album and scissors and lots of glue.

